  "当前还没有可用的下游配置快照。请先确保 Authority 已成功连接 OpenClaw，然后刷新运行时。": "There is currently no downstream configuration snapshot available. Please first ensure that Authority has successfully connected to OpenClaw, then refresh the runtime.",
  "当前还没有可展示的协作回流。进入需求房后，派单和成员回复会回流到这里。": "There are currently no collaborative reflows to demonstrate. After entering the demand room, dispatch orders and member replies will flow back here.",
